  <p class="para">gnupg 标识符，由对<span class="function">{@link gnupg_init()}</span> 或 <span class="classname"><strong class="classname">gnupg</strong></span> 的调用生成。</p>     </dd>             <dt><span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">plaintext</span></dt>     <dd>      <p class="para">       The text being encrypted.      </p>     </dd>       </dl>   </div> <div class="refsect1 returnvalues" id="refsect1-function.gnupg-encryptsign-returnvalues">  <h3 class="title">返回值</h3>  <p class="para">   On success, this function returns the encrypted and signed text.   On failure, this function returns <strong><span><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/reserved.constants.php#constant.false">false</a></span></strong>.  </p> </div> <div class="refsect1 examples" id="refsect1-function.gnupg-encryptsign-examples">  <h3 class="title">示例</h3>  <p class="para">   </p><div class="example" id="example-3403">    <p><strong>示例 #1 Procedural <span class="function"><strong>gnupg_encryptsign()</strong></span> example</strong></p>    <div class="example-contents"><div class="phpcode" style="border-color:gray;background:#1E1F22;"><blockquote style="border:1px gray solid;white-space:pre-wrap"><span style="color: #000000"><span style="color: #9876AA">&lt;?php<br>$res </span><span style="color: #007700">= </span><span style="color: #9876AA">gnupg_init</span><span style="color: #007700">();<br></span><span style="color: #9876AA">gnupg_addencryptkey</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$res</span><span style="color: #007700">,</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"8660281B6051D071D94B5B230549F9DC851566DC"</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br></span><span style="color: #9876AA">gnupg_addsignkey</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$res</span><span style="color: #007700">,</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"8660281B6051D071D94B5B230549F9DC851566DC"</span><span style="color: #007700">,</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"test"</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br></span><span style="color: #9876AA">$enc </span><span style="color: #007700">= </span><span style="color: #9876AA">gnupg_encryptsign</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$res</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #DD0000">"just a test"</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br>echo </span><span style="color: #9876AA">$enc</span><span style="color: #007700">;<br></span><span style="color: #9876AA">?&gt;</span></span></blockquote></div>    </div>   </div>   <div class="example" id="example-3404">    <p><strong>示例 #2 OO <span class="function"><strong>gnupg_encryptsign()</strong></span> example</strong></p>    <div class="example-contents"><div class="phpcode" style="border-color:gray;background:#1E1F22;"><blockquote style="border:1px gray solid;white-space:pre-wrap"><span style="color: #000000"><span style="color: #9876AA">&lt;?php<br>$gpg </span><span style="color: #007700">= new </span><span style="color: #9876AA">gnupg</span><span style="color: #007700">();<br></span><span style="color: #9876AA">$gpg</span><span style="color: #007700">-&gt;</span><span style="color: #9876AA">addencryptkey</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"8660281B6051D071D94B5B230549F9DC851566DC"</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br></span><span style="color: #9876AA">$gpg</span><span style="color: #007700">-&gt;</span><span style="color: #9876AA">addsignkey</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"8660281B6051D071D94B5B230549F9DC851566DC"</span><span style="color: #007700">,</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"test"</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br></span><span style="color: #9876AA">$enc </span><span style="color: #007700">= </span><span style="color: #9876AA">$gpg</span><span style="color: #007700">-&gt;</span><span style="color: #9876AA">encryptsign</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #D