/**
* <div id="function.gnupg-seterrormode" class="refentry"> <div class="refnamediv">  <h1 class="refname">gnupg_seterrormode</h1>  <p class="verinfo">(PECL gnupg &gt;= 0.6)</p><p class="refpurpose"><span class="refname">gnupg_seterrormode</span> — <span class="dc-title">Sets the mode for error_reporting</span></p> </div> <div class="refsect1 description" id="refsect1-function.gnupg-seterrormode-description">  <h3 class="title">说明</h3>  <div class="methodsynopsis dc-description">   <span class="methodname" style="color:#CC7832"><strong>gnupg_seterrormode</strong></span>(<span class="methodparam"><span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.resource.php" class="type resource" style="color:#EAB766">resource</a></span> <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">$identifier</span></span>, <span class="methodparam"><span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.integer.php" class="type int" style="color:#EAB766">int</a></span> <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">$errormode</span></span>): <span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.void.php" class="type void" style="color:#EAB766">void</a></span></div>  <p class="para rdfs-comment">   Sets the mode for <a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/errorfunc.configuration.php#ini.error-reporting" class="link">error_reporting</a>.  </p> </div> <div class="refsect1 parameters" id="refsect1-function.gnupg-seterrormode-parameters">  <h3 class="title">参数</h3>  <p class="para">   </p><dl>         <dt><span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">identifier</span></dt>     <dd>      <p class="para">gnupg 标识符，由对<span class="function">{@link gnupg_init()}</span> 或 <span class="classname"><strong class="classname">gnupg</strong></span> 的调用生成。</p>     </dd>             <dt><span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">errormode</span></dt>     <dd>      <p class="para">       The error mode.      </